<DIV style="position:absolute;top:275;left:144"><nobr><span class="ft7">The following are the major submarkets and representative vendors for the content<br>access tools market:</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:329;left:144"><nobr><span class="ft0">! </span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:329;left:171"><nobr><span class="ft0">Search engines, platforms, and applications</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:362;left:144"><nobr><span class="ft0">! </span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:362;left:171"><nobr><span class="ft0">Text mining and text analytics</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:395;left:144"><nobr><span class="ft0">! </span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:395;left:171"><nobr><span class="ft0">Browsing and guided navigation</span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:428;left:144"><nobr><span class="ft0">! </span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:428;left:171"><nobr><span class="ft0">Categorizers</span></nobr></DIV>
