<DIV style="position:absolute;top:1023;left:545"><nobr><span class="ft17">$$$$% high, </span></nobr></DIV>
<DIV style="position:absolute;top:1023;left:648"><nobr><span class="ft17">$$$$$ very high</span></nobr></DIV>
